                <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-2">Sebaiknya dicek lebih dulu.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-yellow-200 shadow-lg p-6">
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Peringatan</p>
